ng that your life and lives of people like you are worthy of being told thought about discussed and even celebrated” “the multicultural children’s book segment in the united states is one of the biggest untapped markets” says beasley  kazoom gives kickstarter backers not only the opportunity to support a cause but also to become a character in a book or to tell their life story i personally think it is pretty exciting to have a children’s book written around your life story or that of someone you love don’t you think so” comments are closed order now are you ready to submit your press release to top news search engines national newspapers radio stations and news channelssubmit your press release today why use lightning releases  access top news search engines  maximum distribution  cost effective  seo friendly  easy to use  guaranteed placement click here to learn more testimonials “i have used lightning releases about half a dozen times now it is easy to use and very economical the distribution system works well and we see instant results in searches”  gary davies evp sales and marketing adflow networks “we use lightning releases for all of our press release requirements lightning releases is by far the best price we have found for press releases and we always get fast and courteous service i would recommend giving lightning releases a try for your next release”  micah carlson vice president of marketing at dakota security systems read more testimonials recent releases the narcosocio syndrome in government sound engineer suraj pillai helps bring american tv shows to foreign countries the iguana project accomplished enterprise sales leader craig herman joins insights as vice president sales dais analytic corporation featured on pbs syndicate or subscribe automatically get new fulltext press releases from lightning releases with our rss feed or view all available feeds contact us contact us via email at contact at lightningreleasescom kazoom creating books for multic