asley  backers pledged  to help bring this project to life rewards campaign faq updates  comments  community share this project notify me on launch about this project youll need an html capable browser to see this content play replay with sound play with sound   chicago il childrens books  pledged of  goal  backers what is kazoom kids books  kazoom kids books is creating a digital library of interactive multicultural childrens books for ages  to  our ibook apps will engage a child with readalong narration music animation and interactive technology our goal is to make these books entertaining and enriching for our young readers and to encourage a love of readingwe believe our books build selfesteem by giving children the opportunity to see themselves in the story’s characters and then mirror the characters curiosity and courage we believe every child should see themselves and their community in a book  why kazoom kids books if you are an africanamerican or hispanic mother of young children you can seldom find children’s books that reflect your life family and community there is a void in the publishing industry for multicultural children’s books it is a startling fact that  of childrens literature does not include children of color  of the  children’s books published in  only  featured children of color yet both our public schools and our country are growing more culturally diverse each year and many of the most popular books for black children available on amazon today were published  to  years agowho writes and illustrates our booksone of the challenges of creating multicultural kids books is that many of the interested talented writers and illustrators have not been able to get into the field of childrens books because major publishing houses dont publish these kinds of diverse books or hire multicultural writrers when they do  here is a surprising statistic last year just  of the   childrens books about africanamericans were actually written andor illustrated by african americans at kazoom were opening our doors to talented writers across all multicultural communitiesso we went out into the community and asked writers and artists to help us create greater diversity in childrens books and many of them said yes as a result we are a company that is for the community and by the communitywhy diversity is important in childrens books   it helps a child to gain a better understanding of themselvesbooks are a powerful way for getting children to understand their family neighborhood and the world in which they live multicultural books have been proven to have a positive development effect on children of all backgrounds children can learn to respect other cultural groups and even celebrate their differences  books by black and latino authors limit stereotype portrayals of characters and situationswhy we need your help help us create greater diversity in children’s literature we need the funding in order to produce the best books we can  with your support we will be able to finalize the production of our books which includes hiring local writers and artists to illustrate books and hiring the interactive book designers and recording of the readalong narration  finalize our custom app to incorporate both our library of books and the player that allows customers to easily play our interactive books on their android or apple devicesplease help us continue producing highquality books and enjoy a variety of cool backer rewards what’s inside our books each book in the kazoom kids digital library consists of stories with full color pages featuring children from diverse backgrounds solving problems trying new things and fearlessly exploring the world our books have readalong narration interactive action and animation when kids have a healthy selfesteem a sense of fearless possibility is inspired the characters in kazoom kids books are no different they use selfesteem to give them courage to try new things make new friends and barge into new adventures with a sense of wonder our books help children enjoy reading by adding sound motion and animation to the stories in a fun and engaging way the beautiful artwork is accurate to multicultural communities neighborhoods and experiences the text is fun to read and easy to understand and each book has readalong narration which helps kids learn new words and phrases with ease  kazoom kids books makes great stories accessible to all you dont have to be a child of color to enjoy these books each story weaves narration beautiful illustrations and positive messages together to celebrate the power of differences and inclusion  our digital libraryour library allows children to engage with books in new ways our books have great stories  that allows kids to engage with stories at their own pace and build a bigger vocabulary beautiful illustrations by talented artists readalong narration  that provides a fun way to build word and sound development and stimulate language skills   interactive books  that allows kids to engage with the characters in enjoyable stories they will love the library gives kids the opportunity to use different sensory skills all at once to better comprehend and recognize new words and understand new ideas easilymeet our amazing team drawing from our collective   years experience in publishing advertising and mobile design development as well as our education childrearing storytelling artmaking and corporate experience you can trust us to bring you engaging highquality books with stories that are relevant long after the pages are closed  risks and challenges  this is a large multiple book project we are creating several books which is more challenging than a single story we do however have the best talented creative team to develop these beautiful books donna is an experienced publisher who has solid experience producing multiple children’s book projects the first books are near completion we are confident that with this funding we can finalize and deliver the first  interactive digital books this summer  our books rely on technology our books rely on technology and sometimes technology can fail but our apps and digital library are on a secured cloud platform for an easy user friendly customer experience our library book app will be available in the both the google play and apple itunes stores  telling your story perks includes your timing the timing to deliver the “tell your story” perk is estimated it depends on your availability for the interview and the illustrator’s time to develop illustrations on average  months is sufficient time to complete your story thank you so much in advance for helping us to create greater diversity in children’s books you’re helping make a difference in the lives of thousands of children learn about accountability on kickstarter questions about this project check out the faq report this project to kickstarter support this project select this reward pledge  or more about  a big virtual hug thank you for your support every dollar counts well list you as a supporter on our facebook page less estimated delivery jun   backers pledge amount  continue other payment options kickstarter is not a store its a way to bring creative projects to life learn more about accountability select this reward pledge  or more about  digital screensaver an illustrated digital background screensaver for your phone tablet or computer featuring a scene or characters from one of our books and well list you as a supporter on our facebook page less estimated delivery jun   backers pledge amount  continue other payment options kickstarter is not a store its a way to bring creative projects to life learn more about accountability select this reward pledge  or more about  digital ebook receive a digital ebook not interactive of one of our childrens books and well list you as a supporter on our facebook page less estimated delivery jun   backers pledge amount  continue other payment options kickstarter is not a s